OL,3,CCouncil racks up #1.85 billion of debt
OL,4,Cas inspectors brought in to help
OL,6,FThe government has ordered an
OL,7,Finvestigation into Borough Council as
OL,8,Ffigures reveal it is almost #1.85
OL,9,Fbillion debt.
OL,11,FIt follows a report which found the
OL,12,Fcouncil is the most indebted unitary
OL,13,Fauthority in the country, with "their
OL,14,Fportfolio of debt-funded
OL,15,Finvestments... concerning" which put
OL,16,Fnot only the council at risk, but
OL,17,Fcould also have "significant impact"
OL,18,Ffor local residents.
