OL,6,FThe report also raised "some concerns
OL,7,Fwith decision-making, governance and
OL,8,Foversight".
OL,10,FSimon Hoare, the Minister for Local
OL,11,FGovernment, announced the 'best value'
OL,12,Finspection on 8 May which will see an
OL,13,Finspector investigate whether the
OL,14,Fcouncil can work to control its debt
OL,15,Fand reduce it over time.
OL,17,FThe council says the move will have no
OL,18,Fimpact on its day-to-day operations.
