OL,7,FAndy Carter he said the knock on for
OL,8,Fthose living in the area could be
OL,9,F"significant".
OL,11,F"The downside for local residents if
OL,12,Fthese investments do go wrong is about
OL,13,F#10,000 per household, that's a really
OL,14,Fsignificant level of risk for every
OL,15,Fhousehold in Warrington," he said.
