OL,6,F"We're seeing that in Birmingham where
OL,7,Fdecisions were taken by the City
OL,8,FCouncil and we're now seeing council
OL,9,Ftax is going up by 20% to pay off
OL,10,Fthose decisions, we've got to be
OL,11,Freally aware in Warrington that the
OL,12,Fdecisions taken by Labour in the town
OL,13,Fhall are with public money, not
OL,14,Fshareholders money, and that risk
OL,15,Ffalls to the public, the tax payers in
OL,16,FWarrington."
OL,18,FHe welcomed the inspection, adding he
OL,19,Fhas been warning people about the
OL,20,Fdangers from the "reckless decisions"
OL,21,Ffor some time.
