OL,6,FHe added: "I have been warning this
OL,7,Fwould happen, the council have
OL,8,Fborrowed a sum of money, #1.8 billion,
OL,9,Fand what we've seen over the last few
OL,10,Fweeks is significant evidence of
OL,11,Freckless decisions with organisations
OL,12,Fgoing bust, investments into
OL,13,Fproperties which are making losses,
OL,14,Fand even investments into junk bonds
OL,15,Fwhich are causing losses for the
OL,16,Fcouncil.
