OL,6,FIn response, the council's cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for corporate finance, Labour
OL,8,Fcouncillor Denis Matthews said the
OL,9,Freport, available online "presents a
OL,10,Fvery different picture".
OL,12,FThe issue is raised at Prime
OL,13,FMinister's Questions by MP Andy Carter.
OL,15,FBut, the council's cabinet member for
OL,16,Fcorporate finance at the time, Cllr
OL,17,FDenis Matthews, denied the authority
OL,18,Fwas heading "towards bankruptcy".
