OL,6,FHe said: "It is time we had an honest
OL,7,Fconversation about the council's
OL,8,Fborrowing and investments.
OL,10,F"For too long the message pushed out
OL,11,Fby many is that Warrington Borough
OL,12,FCouncil has massive debt, and that we
OL,13,Fare heading towards bankruptcy. This
OL,14,Fis simply not true."
OL,16,FHe added that the council had invested
OL,17,Fmoney because it had been told by the
OL,18,Fnational Conservative government "they
OL,19,Fshould look to find other sources of
OL,20,Fincome generation".
